data.description: Welcome home! This home is located in Joshua, Texas, and is only 20-25 minutes from downtown Ft. Worth! This home has just over 2,100 sq feet, 3 beds, and 2 full baths along with a study option that could be converted into an extra bedroom if need be, making 4 beds total. Right as you walk in you will notice wood floors throughout all the living areas in the home. Granite countertops, custom cabinets, and stainless steel appliances will make this kitchen perfect for today’s trends. This floor plan also supports a very open layout perfect for hosting guests! Located in Joshua ISD! Look no more this is it! HOME TO BE COMPLETED END OF MARCH TO MID APRIL
